msgctxt "Talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hello there, traveler. Welcome to\n"
"our <2.se_co>stable<3.re_co>. You will stay awhile,\n"
"won't you?\n"
"If you have a horse, we can help you\n"
"change its <4.se_co>gear<5.re_co> or <6.se_co>mane<7.re_co> style.\n"
"\n"
"<8.so>We're always happy to meet new horses,\n"
"so stop on by!"
msgstr ""

