"<1.so>Hello there! That's a mighty fine horse\n"
"you have.\n"
"\n"
"If you like, I can change out its <2.se_co>gear<3.re_co>\n"
"or maybe...<4.ra><5.pa><6.ra>\n"
"\n"
"<7.so>Oh? My goodness, that's no pony, is it?\n"
"It's so big!\n"
"\n"
"<8.so>I'm sorry, but I don't think I have any\n"
"<9.se_co>gear <10.re_co>that'd fit such a large horse, and I\n"
"bet it wouldn't like its <11.se_co>mane<12.re_co> handled...\n"
"<13.so>I'm so sorry about that."
msgstr ""

